<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA April 18. -- A delegation of the Ministry 
for Foreign Affairs led by Deputy Minister Nguyen Dy Nien has 
paid a visit to the Islamic Republic of Iran. 
  While in Iran, the delegation was received by Iranian 
Foreign 
Minister 'Ali Akbar Velayati, held by Deputy Minister (Mahdi 
Mostafavi). [sentence as received] The two sides exchanged 
views on orientation and measures to promote the cooperative 
