<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Quang Ninh Province Opens Border Gate With PRC </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Quang Ninh Province Opens Border Gate With PRC </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1804141794 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 18 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1804141794 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A ceremony has been held in Quang Ninh Province on 
the opening of the border gate between Vietnam and China. The 
Bac Luong bridge, 135 meters long, links the Vietnamese district 
of Mong Cai with Tunhung [as heard] Province in China. The 
bridge was built by both sides in 1992. 
  People from both Vietnam and China have been waiting for the 
opening of the border gate and the construction of Bac Luong 
bridge. 
  After the ceremony, Vietnamese and Chinese peoples paid 
visit 
to each other in a friendly, peaceful, and cooperative 
atmosphere. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

