<H3> <TI>   Foreign Party Delegations Wrap Up Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Party Delegations Wrap Up Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Performers Tour Pyongyang </H4>

<F P=102> SK1804111394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1028 GMT 18 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1804111394 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 18 (KCNA) -- Artistes of foreign 
countries who have participated in the 12th April Spring 
Friendship Art Festival visited various places during their stay 
in Pyongyang. 
  They visited Mangyongdae, the cradle of revolution, where 
the 
great leader President Kim Il-song was born. 
  With deep emotion and pleasure of visiting the sacred place 
of revolution, they enthusiastically sang in front of the old 
home the songs "Song of General Kim Il-song" and "Let Us Sing of 
Spring Holiday of April" carrying boundless respect and 
reverence for President Kim Il-song who is making an undying 
contribution to accomplishing the cause of global independence. 
  They went to the tower of the chuche idea, the arch of 
triumph, the three revolutions exhibition and others. 
  Vice-minister of Culture of Egypt Abdul Rahman Abdul Farah, 
said the tower of the chuche idea was a monumental edifice which 
has been built so splendidly. He went on: 
  Through the visit, I have come to know well where is the 
source of the Korean people's fortitude. 
  It is because the Korean people are firmly armed with the 
chuche idea. 
  I wish greater success to the struggle of the Korean people 
who are advancing forward under the banner of the chuche idea. 
  The artistes appreciated the mass gymnastic display "Great 
Victory of Rural Theses" and participated in the evening dancing 
party of youth and students in Pyongyang and celebrations of 
April 15. 

</TEXT>

