Indonesian people's support for the Iraqi people in facing the 
unfair blockade imposed on them. He also expressed hope that 
the blockade will be lifted as soon as possible. 
  Salih arrived in Jakarta from the Philippines today on an 
official visit to Indonesia lasting several days at the 
invitation of the Indonesian Parliament. 

