  [Text] Tokyo, April 17 (KNS-KCNA) -- The Federation of 
South Koreans in Japan for Democracy and Reunification, the 
League of South Korean Youth in Japan and the Democratic 
Association of South Korean Women in Japan recently issued a 
joint appeal calling on the 70 million Koreans at home and 
