voices and hold higher the banner of struggle in order to oppose 
the resumption of the Team Spirit joint military maneuvers, 
check the shipment of Patriot missiles and frustrate all the 
military provocations," said the appeal. "All the Koreans who 
love the country and the nation should join hands and kindle the 
flames of the anti-U.S., anti-war and anti-nuke struggle." 

