<H3> <TI>   Ramos Meets Visiting Iraqi Assembly Speaker </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ramos Meets Visiting Iraqi Assembly Speaker </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2004164994 Baghdad INA in English 1350 GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN2004164994 </F>
