Il-song in Austria in a statement strongly demanded that the 
United States give up the scheme to resume the Team Spirit joint 
military exercises and the deployment of Patriot in South Korea 
and immediately stop all its hostile acts against the DPRK. 
  The Congolese committee to support the proposal for founding 
the Democratic Confederal Republic of Koryo in an appeal to the 
peaceloving people of the world called on them to heighten 
vigilance against the anti-DPRK campaign of the United States 
and denounce it. 

