BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, April 20 (KNS-KCNA) -- A central meeting of 
Korean youth and students in Japan was held at the Shiba Park in 
Tokyo on April 19 to denounce the nuclear war provocation moves 
of the U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppet clique and 
pave the way of peace of the country and its reunification on 
the occasion of the 34th anniversary of the April 19 popular 
uprising in South Korea. 
  Present were So Man-sul, vice-chairman of the Central 
Standing Committee of the General Association of Korean 
Residents in Japan (Chongnyon), and some 2,000 Korean youths and 
