  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 20 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- At the 
invitation of the Prime Minister of Mongolia P. Jasray the 
Premier of the State Council of the People's Republic of China 
Li Peng will arrive in Mongolia on an official visit on 28-29 
April of the current year. 
