negotiations. The Chinese premier will call on the President of 
Mongolia P. Ochirbat and the Chairman of the Great State Hural 
of Mongolia Bagabandi. In the course of the visit it is 
expected that the Mongolian-Chinese Treaty on Friendly Relations 
and Cooperation be signed as well as the intergovernmental 
agreements on cooperation in the spheres of culture and 
veterinary service and the protection and use of border rivers 
waters, informed the press office of the Ministry of External 
Relations of Mongolia. 

