<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Program Marks Lenin's Birthday, Hails Socialism </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Program Marks Lenin's Birthday, Hails Socialism </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2104092794 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1400 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2104092794 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ("Topical Talk" feature with station editor Vu Dinh Vinh] </F>
  [Excerpt] [Passage omitted on Lenin's concepts in 
proletarianism and his work and devotion that resulted in the 
victory of the Great Russian October Revolution and the setting 
up of the first socialist state in the world] Dear comrades and 
friends, in commemorating the 124th birthday of Lenin, we should 
study his work and devotion to clearly understand his concepts. 
This will help us to have a correct stand in the current 
politico- ideological struggle. For this reason, our party has 
encouraged systematic studies on achievements and failure of the 
international communist and worker's movement, especially the 
collapse of socialism in Eastern Europe and the former Soviet 
Union. Through these studies we will clearly understand the 
real concepts of Marxism-Leninism to be able to renovate our 
thought to bring the doctrine into full play, thus catching up 
with developments of the era. At the same time, we will be able 
to uphold the Ho Chi Minh thought and promote socialism to 
formulate measures and orientations for our revolution in the 
current stage. 
  Our party's basic lines and policies are to renovate thought 
and concept while striving to oppose opportunism and revision 
and overcoming conservatism and dogmatism. 
  It is necessary to say that we are facing numerous 
difficulties in the politico-ideological struggle. As a result, 
we must strive to maintain and develop all favorable conditions 
to win in the struggle. The most fundamental favorable feature 
of our just cause rests with Marxism-Leninism and Ho Chi Minh 
thought. Although efforts are being made to study and overcome 
weaknesses in socialist concepts, achievements of the renovation 
process have testified to our correct application of 
Marxism-Leninism and Ho Chi Minh thought, especially in the 
current complicated changes at home and abroad. 
  Today, in commemorating great Lenin's birthday anniversary, 
we recall a foreign scholar's expression: Amid crises, there 
existed persons of genius who created historical events, such as 
Lenin and Ho Chi Minh. Indeed, they have written an 
unforgettable history despite changes and developments. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

